5\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"411\" data-end=\"465\">Cost per engagement (CPE) ranges from KSh 6\u201320<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"466\" data-end=\"542\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"468\" data-end=\"542\">Cost per click (CPC) for traffic campaigns falls between KSh 20\u201360<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"543\" data-end=\"653\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"545\" data-end=\"653\">Daily budget recommendations start at KSh 5,000 for test campaigns, scaling upwards based on results<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"655\" data-end=\"757\">Aminifu Digital helps you define an efficient budget, set realistic KPIs, and optimise spend in real time.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;What formats perform best on the platform?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715360052312-795bf34f-889a82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"817\" data-end=\"870\">The best-performing ad formats on X in Kenya include:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"871\" data-end=\"1224\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"871\" data-end=\"928\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"873\" data-end=\"928\"><strong data-start=\"873\" data-end=\"892\">Promoted Tweets<\/strong>: Great for engagement and awareness<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"929\" data-end=\"1036\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"931\" data-end=\"1036\"><strong data-start=\"931\" data-end=\"960\">Video Ads (15\u201330 seconds)<\/strong>: High engagement and better click-throughs when paired with strong captions<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1037\" data-end=\"1124\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1039\" data-end=\"1124\"><strong data-start=\"1039\" data-end=\"1061\">Follower Campaigns<\/strong>: Ideal for brand accounts looking to build an active community<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1125\" data-end=\"1224\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1127\" data-end=\"1224\"><strong data-start=\"1127\" data-end=\"1146\">Promoted Trends<\/strong>: Most effective for campaigns tied to national events or days of significance<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1226\" data-end=\"1341\">We\u2019ll help you select the format based on your specific goals \u2014 whether it\u2019s visibility, engagement, or conversion.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;Can I retarget users who engaged with my tweets?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361191995-ff8a0d69-1fe982d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1407\" data-end=\"1455\">Yes. X allows advertisers to retarget users who:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1456\" data-end=\"1589\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1456\" data-end=\"1492\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1458\" data-end=\"1492\">Viewed or engaged with your tweets<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1493\" data-end=\"1537\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1495\" data-end=\"1537\">Clicked on links or interacted with videos<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1538\" data-end=\"1589\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1540\" data-end=\"1589\">Visited your website (with proper tracking setup)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1591\" data-end=\"1739\">We configure X\u2019s retargeting capabilities using <strong data-start=\"1639\" data-end=\"1690\">pixel tracking and custom audience segmentation<\/strong>, ensuring your ads follow through to conversion.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;Do I need a large following to run ads?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361240947-6ed290f2-a03582d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1796\" data-end=\"1990\">No \u2014 your follower count has no impact on your ability to run ads. You can promote tweets from accounts with <strong data-start=\"1905\" data-end=\"1928\">no followers at all<\/strong>. That said, having an active, credible profile helps improve:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1991\" data-end=\"2102\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1991\" data-end=\"2031\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1993\" data-end=\"2031\">Ad performance and click-through rates<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2032\" data-end=\"2059\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2034\" data-end=\"2059\">User trust and engagement<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2060\" data-end=\"2102\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2062\" data-end=\"2102\">Cost efficiency (better relevance score)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2104\" data-end=\"2187\">As part of our service, we optimise your brand\u2019s profile for advertising readiness.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;Can you run political or advocacy campaigns on X?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361291476-30b845c7-304f82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2254\" data-end=\"2347\">Yes, we can. However, X (like all major platforms) requires:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2348\" data-end=\"2519\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2348\" data-end=\"2408\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2350\" data-end=\"2408\"><strong data-start=\"2350\" data-end=\"2371\">Proper disclosure<\/strong> for political or issue-based content<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2409\" data-end=\"2466\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2411\" data-end=\"2466\"><strong data-start=\"2411\" data-end=\"2466\">Compliance with local laws and platform regulations<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2467\" data-end=\"2519\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2469\" data-end=\"2519\"><strong data-start=\"2469\" data-end=\"2519\">Verified account information and documentation<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2521\" data-end=\"2659\">Aminifu Digital Agency supports NGOs, civic bodies, and advocacy groups in compliant campaign setup, messaging, and distribution strategy.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;How do you measure success on X campaigns?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1743526712886-b4454e14-6759&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2723\" data-end=\"2780\">We go beyond vanity metrics. Success is measured through:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2781\" data-end=\"2973\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2781\" data-end=\"2815\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2783\" data-end=\"2815\">Impressions and engagement rates<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2816\" data-end=\"2852\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2818\" data-end=\"2852\">Cost per result (CPC, CPE, or CPV)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2853\" data-end=\"2900\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2855\" data-end=\"2900\">Web traffic tracked via <strong data-start=\"2879\" data-end=\"2900\">UTM codes and GA4<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2901\" data-end=\"2973\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2903\" data-end=\"2973\">Actionable insights like replies, quote tweets, and sentiment analysis<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2975\" data-end=\"3052\">You receive a full report and strategic recommendations after every campaign.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;Can you also help with strategy and creative?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1743526791148-b65e2d70-0687&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3214\" data-end=\"3300\">Yes. Our service includes everything from strategy, targeting setup, creative design, copywriting, and ongoing optimisation \u2014 so you don\u2019t need to manage any part of the process in-house.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][\/vc_tta_accordion][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; content_placement=&#8221;middle&#8221; type=&#8221;vc_default&#8221; margin_top=&#8221;5&#8243; margin_bottom=&#8221;10&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1716548610536{padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom